{"article_id":"xNEQrvTvg2aOfMAa","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Leaked NSA documents","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"revealing","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"that Russia engaged in election-related hacking efforts just days before the election","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"directly contradict what former President Barack Obama told the American public .","depth":2},{"id":4,"text":"Speaking at a year-end news conference in December ,","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"Obama told the public","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"that Russian interference in the election ceased","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"after he told Russian President Vladimir Putin to \" cut it out \" in early September .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"Russia ' s cyberattacks stopped after warnings of \" serious consequences \"","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"if they continued ,","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"Obama said .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"\" What I was concerned about in particular was making sure","depth":12},{"id":12,"text":"[ the DNC hack ] wasn ' t compounded by potential hacking","depth":13},{"id":13,"text":"that could hamper vote counting ,","depth":14},{"id":14,"text":"affect the actual election process itself , \"","depth":14},{"id":15,"text":"Obama said .","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"\" So in early September","depth":13},{"id":17,"text":"when I saw President Putin in China ,","depth":13},{"id":18,"text":"I felt","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"that the most effective way","depth":13},{"id":20,"text":"to ensure that that didn ' t happen","depth":13},{"id":21,"text":"was to talk to him directly","depth":13},{"id":22,"text":"and tell him to cut it out","depth":14},{"id":23,"text":"and there were going to be serious consequences","depth":15},{"id":24,"text":"if he didn ' t .","depth":15},{"id":25,"text":"And in fact we did not see further tampering of the election process . \"","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"\" But the leaks through WikiLeaks had already occurred , \"","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"Obama said ,","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"indicating","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"that any further election interference was the result of emails","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"released by WikiLeaks in the days and weeks","depth":14},{"id":31,"text":"leading up to the election .","depth":14},{"id":32,"text":"\" The president made it sound like that worked , \"","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"The New York Times reported at the time ,","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"noting Obama ' s claim","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"that \" we did not see further tampering of the election process . \"","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"But NSA documents","depth":13},{"id":37,"text":"published by The Intercept on Monday","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"revealed","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"that as late as October 31 or November 1 , hackers launched an election-related spearfishing operation","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"\" targeting U.S. local government organizations . \"","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"In other words , Russia was still tampering with the American electoral process","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"after Obama said","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"they ceased doing so .","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"The documents ' authenticity has been confirmed by U.S. officials ,","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"and the U.S. Department of Justice charged on Monday the woman","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"who leaked the Top Secret documents to The Intercept .","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"\" The NSA assessed","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"that this phase of the spear-fishing operation was likely launched on either October 31 or November 1","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"and sent spear-fishing emails to 122 email addresses","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"' associated with named local government organizations , '","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"probably to officials '","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"involved in the management of voter registration systems , ' \"","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"The Intercept reported .","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"The leaked documents reveal","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"that two other election-related hacking efforts were launched in October","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"-","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"one month after Putin supposedly \" cut it out . \"","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"The success of the hacking operations is unclear ,","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"but their existence appears to directly contradict Obama ' s claim","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"that his warning to Putin resulted in no further election-related meddling .","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"Furthermore , the leaks indicate","depth":5},{"id":62,"text":"that Russia went after the exact target","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"- voting processes -","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"that Obama supposedly stopped them from targeting .","depth":6},{"id":65,"text":"Obama ' s claim","depth":6},{"id":66,"text":"that he pressured Putin into ceasing tampering with the American electoral process","depth":6},{"id":67,"text":"came amid criticisms","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"that his softness on Russia was to blame in part for the nation ' s meddling in the election .","depth":6},{"id":69,"text":"It was only after Donald Trump ' s electoral victory that Obama levied sanctions against the Russians .","depth":6},{"id":70,"text":"President Trump is expected to uphold those sanctions .","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"One month after his inauguration , President Trump questioned","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"whether Obama was \" too soft on Russia . \"","depth":6},{"id":73,"text":"Lisa Monaco , one of Obama ' s top national security advisers , previously told Politico","depth":6},{"id":74,"text":"that the Obama administration sought to downplay Russian interference before the election","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"in order to not further Russia ' s goal","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"of undermining confidence in the election","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"just before it was supposed to take place .","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"\" Our focus was really to make sure","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"that the election process was not undermined ,","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"because here ' s the thing :","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"Whatever else was a subject of debate about motive ,","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"we knew ,","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"and everyone agreed ,","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"that one of the goals","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"that Russia had in all of this","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"was to undermine confidence in our democratic process ,","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"to sow discord ,","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"to sow confusion , \"","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"Monaco said .","depth":6},{"id":90,"text":"But that would not explain why Obama appears to have given misleading statements to the public in December","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"-","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"after the election took place .","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"Despite Obama ' s reassurances","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"that Russia ' s best efforts were not enough","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"to alter actual vote totals ,","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"recent polling has shown","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"that a majority of Democratic voters don ' t believe him .","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"A startling 58 percent of Democratic voters believe","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"Russia actually tampered with vote totals","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"in order to get Trump elected","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"- an outlandish conspiracy theory","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"that remains unsupported by evidence .","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"( RELATED :","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"58 Percent Of Dems Think","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"Russia Rigged Vote Count","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"To Get Trump Elected )","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":213,"left":110,"right":212,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":110,"left":109,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":109,"left":0,"right":108,"re